data.description: CITY & BAY VIEWS From this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home in Hillcrest School District with a 40 year roof installed in 2008. The primary suite offers a walk-in closet, full en suite bath, and private balcony to take in the view!  Main level offers 2 bedrooms & a full bath. The living room features high ceilings, pellet stove, sliding door onto LARGE DECK with expansive BAY & CITY VIEWS! The centrally located kitchen, Laundry and attached garage that is finished off with wall & ceiling drywall & taped. Located near shopping, entertainment, and downtown North Bend.  Currently occupied, please do not disturb occupant, contact your favorite realtor for a tour or listing agent for virtual tour. *Some photos digitally enhanced to remove personal items, and enhance exterior curb appeal*
